<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>. Will write paper on it in next [July] <hi rend="italic">West Riding Asylum Medical Report</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Sends photos of lunatics;</p>
            <p>will send notes corroborative of CD’s views, including some on "hereditarily transmitted movements".</p>
